# CODEOWNERS - Automatic review assignment for XORNG repositories
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owners for everything in the repo
* @XORNG/core-maintainers

# Security-related changes require security team review
SECURITY.md @XORNG/security-team
.github/workflows/security.yml @XORNG/security-team
.github/dependabot.yml @XORNG/security-team

# CI/CD changes require DevOps review
.github/workflows/*.yml @XORNG/devops
Dockerfile @XORNG/devops
docker-compose.yml @XORNG/devops

# Documentation changes
*.md @XORNG/docs-team
documentation/ @XORNG/docs-team

# Configuration files
*.json @XORNG/core-maintainers
*.yml @XORNG/core-maintainers
*.yaml @XORNG/core-maintainers
tsconfig.json @XORNG/core-maintainers

# Source code
src/ @XORNG/core-maintainers
